Gareth Beale 2014-06-19T13:32:49+01:00 2014-06-19T13:32:49+01:00 Registration Open: Digital Heritage 2014 - University of York https://www.jiscmail.ac.uk:443/cgi-bin/webadmin?A2=CODESIGNHERITAGE;15b12520.1406 Dear All,<br><br>Appologies for cross posting. Registration for Digital Heritage 2014 at the<br>University of York is now open. Digital Heritage is an international and<br>interdisciplinary conference for anybody with an interest in the study or<br>representation of the past using digital technology.<br><br>This year theme is 'Digital Communities in Action' and we have a wide range<br>of presentations dealing with the role of communities and concepts of<br>community in Digital Heritage research.
